| Table Type | Description | Attribute |
| --------- | --------- | --------- |
| Standard Sticky                   | Default flex table with sticky headers.        | Default component |
| Nonsticky                         | Default table without sticky headers.          | `unsticky=true` |
| Striped/Borderless/Compact Tables | Tables formatted with classes.                 | `classes='striped borderless compact'` |
| Fixed Table                       | Table does not flex.                           | `fixed='scrollable'` |
| Sortable Table                    | Simple sorting for basic markdown tables       | `sortable=true` |
| Merged Row Headers                | Merged row headers for complex data.           | `grouped=true` |
| No row headers                    | Removes row header indication.  Use sparingly. | `no-row-labels=true` |